<span class="name"><a name="88891"></a></span><span class="postdetails">#1:&nbsp;<font color=black><b>Stupid custom software and stupid Dell</b> Author:&nbsp;<b>Hikaru</b>,&nbsp;</font></span><span class="postdetails"><font color=black></font></span>
<a href="viewtopic.php?p=88891#88891"><img src="templates/subSilver/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails"><font color=black>Posted: Wed Dec 08, 2004 8:34 pm</font><span class="gen"><br>
