<tr><td class="printline">
<span class="postbody">Hikaru,
<br />

<br />
Go into bios and change the com port address.  You should be given options in bios for a range of addresses (com1 through com4)
<br />

<br />
Name Address IRQ 
<br />
COM 1 3F8 4 
<br />
COM 2 2F8 3 
<br />
COM 3 3E8 4 
<br />
COM 4 2E8 3 
<br />
Standard Port Addresses
<br />

<br />
This is only way to change como port adresses. 
<br />

<br />
Steps:
<br />

<br />
boot pc, log into windoze, remove com1, reboot, go into bios, change address, exit and save changes, log into windoze, add new device.
<br />

<br />
Hope this helps
<br />

<br />
Lox</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
</td></tr>
